Usage: setNet [-help] [-setTermSpecial] -type {regular special} {-file <fileName> | -net <netName>}

-help                       # Prints out the command usage
-file <fileName>            # File Name (string, optional)
-net <netName>              # Net Name (string, optional)
-setTermSpecial             # set term also (bool, optional)
-type {regular special}     # Type (enum, required)